There are othe debugging/overloading functions in apd:

apd_callstack(): dump a call stack at your current place  (very cool)
apd_dump_regular_resources(\$array_ref): fills out an array of the current instatiated regular resources.
apd_dump_persistent_resources(\$array_ref): fills out an array of the current instatiated persistent resources.
override_function(string function_name, string function_args, dtring function_code):  syntax similair to create function().  Overrides built-in functions (replaces them in the symbol table)
rename_function(string orig_name, string new_name):  renames orig_name to new_name in the global function_table.  Useful for temporarly overriding builtin functions.
